examples.en: Just calm down, stop gabbling, and tell me what has happened.
Don't gabble out your story, man, tell it calmly and clearly.
I expect you spent half the day gabbling away with your neighbours.
During the filming of the party scene the extras were told to just gabble and act like they were having a great time.
She heard her parents' guests still gabbling in the living room late into the night.
